OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA day of cloud and rain, the
OL,6,Frain persistent and at times heavy
OL,7,Facross the Peak District, will spread
OL,8,Feastwards across the area through the
OL,9,Fmorning. Becoming breezy, especially
OL,10,Fover western hills. Feeling humid. The
OL,11,Frain easing later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain will clear through the
OL,14,Fevening, leaving a few clear spells,
OL,15,Fespecially in the east, although an
OL,16,Fisolated shower remains possible. Mild
OL,17,Fand breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
